   <body>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA"><a name="DUCc0036718251a100584bdd8c3784850d2"></a>Removing the cylinder heads
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e13535"> </a>Remove the engine from the frame (<a href="44894.html#DUCc6004ac024f010058895df5a40d4efd2">Removing the engine</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e13540"> </a>Remove the cooling system pipes (<a href="44924.html#DUCc06658c8250110058a838a10427928d2">Removing cooling system pipes and unions</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e13545"> </a>Remove the timing outer covers and belts (<a href="45036.html#DUC5af7ddf82516100581d2e6ffb59083d2">Removing the timing outer covers</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e13550"> </a>Refit the intake manifolds (<a href="45080.html#DUC2a6cf570256a10058f958bcf4dec2ed2">Removing intake manifold and water union</a>).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e13556"> </a>Using the tool no. <span class="bold">88713.2676</span>, undo the nuts (1) on the cylinder head stud bolts.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e13561"> </a>Remove the cylinder head nuts (1) and special washers (2).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_9_019101864.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e13566"> </a>Remove the cylinder head assembly by lifting it off the engine stud bolts.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e13568"> </a>Repeat the same procedure for the other cylinder head.
         </div>
      </div>
   </body>
